   novenmaculata, Anobium punctatum and Pissodes castaneus were the first
   species detected. Tomicus spp. (29\%) and Ips sexdentatus (23\%) were
   the dominant taxa. Bole char height and soil burn severity were
   positively correlated with insect presence. Trees with short stem
